# Scope Discipline

- Only make changes the user explicitly asked for.
- Do not fix, restore, or add things you notice are missing unless the user asked you to.
- If you notice something broken or missing, mention it to the user instead of silently fixing it.
- When a task has multiple steps, complete only the requested steps.
